# Core Plugin: Executable Quick Viewer

🔎🧩 A **Nuclr Commander** quick-view plugin for safe, read-only previews of executable files.

Supported formats:
- 🪟 PE / COFF
- 🐧 ELF
- 🍎 Mach-O
- 🍏 Universal / fat Mach-O

What it shows:
- 📋 format, type, architecture, bitness, endianness
- 🧠 entrypoint / image-base / ABI / subsystem details where available
- 🧱 sections or architecture slices
- 🛡️ common flags such as ASLR / NX / PIE where available

It does **not** execute the file and does not rely on native helper tools. ✅

